<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Account Approved — <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f13;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    /* ── Header ── */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 0 32px;
    }
    .logo-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    /* ── Card ── */
    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #141420 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    /* ── Hero banner ── */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b 0%, #312e81 50%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      padding: 48px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.25);
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99,102,241,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .check-circle {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      font-size: 38px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(99,102,241,0.6), 0 0 80px rgba(99,102,241,0.25);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #a5b4fc;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    /* ── Body content ── */
    .content {
      padding: 36px 40px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .greeting strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
    /* ── Feature chips ── */
    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 20px;
      min-width: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .feature-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .feature-text strong { color: #c7d2fe; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    /* ── CTA Button ── */
    .cta-wrap {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0 8px;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(99,102,241,0.5);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    /* ── Divider ── */
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(99,102,241,0.2), transparent);
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 40px 32px;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #6366f1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <!-- Header / Logo -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo-badge">
        <div class="logo-icon">💬</div>
        <span class="logo-text"><%= appName %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Card -->
    <div class="card">
      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="check-circle">✅</div>
        <h1>Account Approved!</h1>
        <p>Your account is now active. Welcome aboard, <%= name %>.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <p class="greeting">
          Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,<br /><br />
          Great news — your <strong><%= appName %></strong> account has been reviewed and 
          <strong style="color:#a5b4fc;">approved</strong> by our team. You now have full 
          access to the platform and can start building right away.
        </p>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Create your first app</strong>
              Head to the dashboard and create your push notification app in seconds.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Start sending notifications</strong>
              Integrate the Vibe Message SDK and start reaching your users instantly.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Monitor your analytics</strong>
              Track notification delivery, engagement, and subscriber growth in real time.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-wrap">
          <a class="cta-btn" href="#">Go to Dashboard →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          You received this email because your account on <strong><%= appName %></strong> was approved.<br />
          If you believe this was a mistake, please <a href="#">contact support</a>.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 8px;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
